ke at the press conference and was adamant that the fighters should not be competing as women.\", \"from\": 1674, \"to\": 2144, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1759, \"end\": 1764, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999706195117739, \"rank\": 2.9381351443277423e-05, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 1799, \"end\": 1807, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"score\": 0.999303941917902, \"rank\": 0.0006127953608981309, \"text\": \"Algerian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\"}, {\"begin\": 1814, \"end\": 1826, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\", \"score\": 0.9999996421621021, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Imane Khelif\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\"}, {\"begin\": 1831, \"end\": 1840, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_Taipei\", \"score\": 0.999999696674468, \"rank\": 2.9403547717422717e-07, \"text\": \"Taiwanese\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_Taipei\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_Taipei\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Medicine is knowledge, it is not opinion,\\\" Filippatos said, adding \\\"One passport can give to us the opportunity to be men, and, tomorrow when I go back to Athens, it's possible to go to my government and\\u2026 change my name from Ioannis Filippatos to Ionnia Filippatos.\", \"from\": 2146, \"to\": 2412, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That means I am a woman tomorrow?\", \"from\": 2413, \"to\": 2446, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Please.\", \"from\": 2447, \"to\": 2454, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The nature and the biological world do not change.\\